<h3>Restorative Justice: Why Do We Need It?</h3>
<p>The film looks at concrete ways to bring the needs of crime survivors into the process of rehabilitating those who commit crimes in order to create a safer society for everyone.  Produced by <a href="https://www.bravenewfilms.org/restorativejustice" target="_blank">Brave New Films</a> and narrated by Danielle Sered of <a href="https://www.commonjustice.org/" target="_blank">Common Justice</a>.</p>

